<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <style>
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        td.spacing {
            font-size: 0;
            width: 0;
        }
        td.body {
          width: 100% !important;
          min-width: 100%;
          padding: 0 !important;
        }
        div.container {
          width: 100%;
          min-width: 100%;
          margin: 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #f6f6f6; font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
    <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; width: 100%;">
      <tr>
        <td class="spacing">&nbsp;</td>
        <td class="body" style="display: block; max-width: 580px; padding: 10px; width: 580px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <div class="container" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 580px; padding: 10px;">
            <table role="presentation" style="background-color: #ffffff; width: 100%;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 20px;">
                  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                    Hey {{.Values.name}},
                  </p>

                  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                    Thank you for registering for our MNCC Bouldering Meetup. We are pleased to confirm your participation!
                  </p>

                  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                    The event will take place on the second Friday of the month. At Minnesota Climbing Cooperative located at 1620 Central Avenue Northeast Minneapolis, MN, 55413. The building entrance is closest to the North West corner of the building facing 18th Ave. There is a entry door near Dock 5. (Just inside the door is the bike storage.) Once you are inside the building go down the hallway to the left keeping an eye out above the doors for the blue and white Minnesota Climbing Cooperative sign.
                  </p>

                  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                    If you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out. We are looking forward to seeing you there!
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>

            <table role="presentation" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px; width: 100%;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                  <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
                    <a href="https://outclimb.gay" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">OutClimb.gay</a> | <a href="mailto:info@outclimb.gay">info@outclimb.gay</a>
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td class="spacing">&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
